IF ccr_a_cortolone_d is MF 0 THEN 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0 AND 2_Normal is MF 1 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 1
IF ccr_thb_d is MF 0 AND ccr_sa_thf_d is MF 1 AND ccr_l6a_oh_dha_d is MF 0 THEN 3_Surpoid is MF 1 AND 2_Normal is MF 0
IF ccr_ll_oxo_etio_d is MF 2 THEN 4_Obese is MF 0 AND 2_Normal is MF 1
